resources.string: This app can track user interactions and certain events on this phone, such as taps on the screen, notifications, what apps are used and how often, clicks on the home / power buttons, and when the screen turns on or off. When enabled, the data is tracked and periodically sent to Siempo\'s servers where it is used to analyze user behavior. You need to activate it below to start the tracking, and you can deactivate it at any time to stop it.
